## Workflow

Work entirely by reading files and writing `memory.md` / `idea.md`. Do not
execute code. For parent runs, inspect `discovered/loss.py`, `notes.md`, and
`run.log`, paying attention to both raw metrics and each normalized value.
Use the island operator to mutate or combine load-bearing mechanisms while
keeping the implementation scoped to `discovered/loss.py`.

